description: The SiteVersion resource allows the creation and management of Avi SiteVersion

tfcfnid.description: Internal identifier for tracking resource changes. Do not use.

Datetime.description: This field represents the creation time of the federateddiff. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

Name.description: Name of the site. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

PrevTargetVersion.description: Previous targer version for a site. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

ReplicationState.description: Replication state for a site. Enum options - REPLICATION_STATE_FASTFORWARD, REPLICATION_STATE_FORCESYNC, REPLICATION_STATE_STREAMING, REPLICATION_STATE_SUSPENDED, REPLICATION_STATE_INIT, REPLICATION_STATE_WAIT, REPLICATION_STATE_NOT_APPLICABLE. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

SiteId.description: Cluster uuid of the site. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

TargetTimeline.description: Target timeline of the site. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

TargetVersion.description: Target version of the site. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

TenantRef.description: Tenant that this object belongs to. It is a reference to an object of type tenant. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

Timeline.description: Timeline of the site. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

Version.description: Version of the site. Field introduced in 20.1.1.

VersionType.description: Type of message for which version is maintained. Enum options - CONFIG_VERSION, HEALTH_STATUS_VERSION. Field introduced in 20.1.1.
